AGI - The Court of Assisi of Mantua has sentenced Dumitru Stratan to 20 years imprisonment for the fetish of Yana Malaiko> aggravated by the affective bond with the girl and for the crime of cloaking of corpse. The judges excluded the aggravating premeditation and, precisely for this reason, the penalty was reduced, as if it had been tried with the abbreviated rite.
The defendant's lawyer, Gregorio Viscomi, had asked for access to the short rite, a possibility that had been denied because the premeditation was hypothesized at the service. The law stipulates that if the premeditation is then excluded at the time of the sentence, the penalty is formulated with the clash of a third of the penalty provided for by the abbreviated judgment.
The twenty-three-year-old Ukrainian of Castiglione delle Stiviere had been killed in his apartment between January 19 and January 2023. Eleven days of uninterrupted research were needed to find it hidden in a sack near an electric power station > under a wood cadaver bordering the province of Brescia. The D.A. called for life sentence for premeditated murder. &nbsp;
